	    <title>Executive Travel: Best Airports for a Long Layover</title>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://www.huffingtonpost.com/executive-travel/best-airports-layover_b_3819040.html" />
    <id>tag:www.huffingtonpost.com,2013:/theblog//3.3819040</id>
    
    <published>2013-09-02T12:18:40Z</published>
    <updated>2013-09-02T12:39:04Z</updated>
    
    <summary>Hours of boredom, cramped seating and stale sandwiches -- layovers are well known to be anything but fun. Here's the good news: A handful of well-managed airports around the world are taking their services and amenities up a serious notch.</summary>
    <author>
        <name>Executive Travel</name>
        <uri>http://www.huffingtonpost.com/executive-travel/</uri>
    </author>
    <content type="html" xml:lang="en" xml:base="http://www.huffingtonpost.com/theblog/">
        &lt;p&gt;Hours of boredom, cramped seating and stale sandwiches -- layovers are well known to be anything but fun. Also, since airlines now fly bigger planes and have reduced the number of flights, layovers have gotten significantly longer.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here's the good news: In response to this woeful trend, a handful of well-managed airports around the world are taking their services and amenities up a serious notch. To see which ones we're talking about, click &lt;a href="http://www.executivetravelmagazine.com/slideshows/best-airports-for-a-long-layover/1" title="Best Airports for a Long Layover" target="_blank"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Singapore's Changi International Airport, for example, has movie theaters, a butterfly garden, a 40-foot slide, a rooftop pool and other fun distractions. Closer to home, San Francisco International Airport receives accolades for well-rounded offerings such as a SFMOMA Museum Store, a distinguished airport museum, a branch of the city's Steinhart Aquarium and seasonally sourced local grub.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To read about our favorite airports for a long layover, click &lt;a href="http://www.executivetravelmagazine.com/slideshows/best-airports-for-a-long-layover/1" title="Best Airports for a Long Layover" target="_blank"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;em&gt;&amp;mdash;Bree Sposato&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

